    R, Rsutdio, Latex - sudo pacman -S r, sudo archlinux-java set java-8-openjdk & pamac install rstudio-desktop, sudo pacman -Syyu texlive-most (unlink("/home/me/src/Rlibs/00LOCK-Rcpp", recursive = TRUE) if failed to lock)
    Texstudio

pin apps to taskbar

